quran[85]{c,v,t}:
  40,1,"Haa, Miim"
  40,2,"Jippagol Deftere nden, ko immorde ka Allah, Foolu…óo, Anndu…óo On"
  40,3,"Haforoowo junubaaji …óin, Ja…ìoowo tuubuubuyee, Sa…ótu…óo lepte, Jom yaajeende. Rewetee…óo alaa, si wanaa kanko. Ko ka Makko woni ruttorde nden"
  40,4,"Alaa ko wennjata e Aayeeje Allah …óen, si wanaa yeddu…ìe …ìen. Wata a hoditor ko …ìe dillirta kon ka leydi"
  40,5,"Ado ma…ì…ìe, yim…ìe Nuuhu …ìen e feddeeji …óin …ìaawo ma…ì…ìe, fennuno (Nulaa…ìe mun …ìen), mofte kala himmiri nanngugol Nulaa…óo mun on. ∆Åe wennjiri meere, fii no bonnitira (goonga) kan. Kono Mi nanngi …ìe. Taskii no nanngal Am ngal wa…ótinirnoo"
  40,6,"Ko wano nii Konngol Joomi maa ngol, jojjiri e yeddu…ìe …ìen : \"Wonnde pellet, ko …ìe yim…ìe Yiite"
  40,7,"∆Åen (Malaa'ikaa…ìe) roondii…ìe Arsiki kin, e won…ìe bannge makki …ìen, hi…ìe subbunhinora yettugol Joomi ma…ì…ìe, …ìe gom…óina Mo, …ìe insinorana gom…óim…ìe …ìen (wiide): \"Joomi amen, A ya√±√±irii kala huunde, yurmeende e ganndal. Yawtan …ìen tuubu…ìe, …ìe jokki laawol Maa ngol, da…óndaa …ìe kadi lepte Dul…ìoowe ngen"
  40,8,"Joomi amen, naadu…ìe ka Aljannaaji √±ii…ìal, …óin …ói fodu…óaa …ìe, e kala mo∆¥∆¥u…óo e baabiraa…ìe ma…ì…ìe, e genndiraa…ìe ma…ì…ìe, e geyngol ma…ì…ìe. Pellet, ko An woni Foolu…óo, √ëee√±u…óo On"
  40,9,"Da…óndaa…ìe [kuu…óe] e bon…óe …óen. Kala mo da…óndu…óaa [kuu…óe] mun bon…óe …óen nden √ëalnde, haray pellet, A yurmiii mo\". Ko …óum woni maloore mawnunde nden"
  40,10,"Yeddu…ìe …ìen noddiroyte: \"Ko tikkere Allah nden …ìuri mawnude, e dii ko tikkan…óon ko'e mon kon, tuma noddeteno…óon e gom…óinal, yeddon"
  40,11,"∆Åe wi'a: \"Joomi amen, A warii men laawi …ói…ói, wuurnitu…óaa men laawi …ói…ói: men qirrike junuubi amen …óin. Taw si laawol yaltirngol hino woodi"
  40,12,"∆äum moo…óon, ko tawde si Allah tun noddanooma, on yeddon; si O kafidaama, gom…óinon. √ëaawoore nden ko Allah heeranii, Toowu…óo, Maw…óo On"
  40,13,"Ko Kanko woni holloowo on maandeeji Makko …óin, O jippinirana on to…ìo ka kammu. Kono taskotaako, si wanaa ruttotoo…óo [e Allah]"
  40,14,"Rewiree Allah, la…ì…ìinirangol Mo diina kan, hay si heefer…ìe …ìen yi…óaa"
  40,15,"Ko o toowu…óo darjaaji, Jey…óo Arsi kin. Himo jippiniria wahayu on, yamiroore Makko, e on mo O muuyani e jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen, no o jertinira √±alnde Kawral ngal, @Corrected"
  40,16,"√±alnde …ìe fee√±oyta. Huunde suu…óotaako Allah, e fee ma…ì…ìe. Ko hommbo laamu woodani hannde? Ko Allah Bajjo, Foolu…óo On"
  40,17,"Hannde, wonkii kala yo…ìete ko faggitii. Too√±e woo alaa hannde, pellet, Allah ko yaawu…óo √±aawoore"
  40,18,"Jertnirt…ìe, √±alaande dillere nden, tuma …ìer…óe …óen ∆¥awtirta ka konondi, hara hi…ìe (heewu…ìe) ngo∆¥o. Gi…óo woo alanaa too√±oo…ìe …ìen, wanaa tefoowo ja…ìantee…óo"
  40,19,"Himo anndi janfa gite, e ko …ìer…óe …óen suu…ói"
  40,20,"Allah ko goonga √±aawirta. ∆äi …ìe rewata …óin non, gaanin Makko, hay huunde …ói √±aawirtaa. Pellet, ko kanko woni Nanoowo, Yi'oowo On"
  40,21,"Hara …ìee yiilaaki ka leydi, …ìe ndaara no battane ado mabbe …ìen wa'unoo? ∆Åen le no …ìurunoo tii…óude doole e batteeji, ka leydi. Allah nanngitiri …ìe junuubi ma…ì…ìe …óin, …ìe he…ìaano da…óndoowo …ìe e (lepte) Allah …óen"
  40,22,"Ko wa…ói …óum, ko tawde Nulaa…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen addayno …ìe …ìanngannduyeeji, …ìe yedda. Allah halki …ìe. Pellet, ko O Doolnu…óo, Sa…ótu…óo lepte"
  40,23,"Gom…óii Men nulirii Muusaa Aayeeje Amen …óen, e hujja …ìanngu…óo"
  40,24,"haa e Fir'awna, e Haamaana, e Qaaruuna. Kono …ìe wi'i: \"Ko mbileejo, …óuu…óu…óo fenaande"
  40,25,"Nde o addannoo …ìe goonga kan, immorde e Amen, …ìe wi'iti: \"Waree …ìi…ó…ìe wor…ìe gom…óimdim…ìe …ìen e makko, accon rew…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen\". Pewje heefer…ìe …ìen wonaali, si wanaa e majjere"
  40,26,"Fir'awna wi'i: \"Accee mi wara Muusaa. Yo o noddu Joomi makko ! Mi…óo huli nde o waylata diina mon kan, maa o fe√±√±ina bonnere ka leydi"
  40,27,"Muusa maaki: \"Mi moolorii Jey…óo lam On, jeyi on, e bone kala mawnintinii…óo, mo gom…óinaa √±alaande hasboore"
  40,28,"Gorko gom…óino…óo goo, jeyaa…óo e yim…ìe Fir'awna …ìen - suu…óunoo…óo gom…óinal mun - :\"E on waray gorko, fii o wi'i: \"Joomi am ko Allah?\" Hara le o addanii on …ìanngannduyeeji, immorde ka Joomi mon. Si tawii o fenu, haray fenaande makko ko kanko fawii; si tawii kadi o goongu, haray yoga e kon ko kammbirani on, he…ìay on\". Pellet, Allah fewnataa on fantinoowo fennoowo"
  40,29,"Ko onon yo yim…ìe am, laamu no woodani on hanndi, ko on foolu…ìe ka leydi. Kono ko hommbo wallata en, e lepte Allah …óen, si …óe arii e men?\" Fir'awna wi'i: \"Mi hollataa on, si wanaa ko mi yi'i kon. Mi tindintaa on kadi, si wanaa e laawol peewal ngol"
  40,30,"Gom…óin…óo on wi'iti: \"Ko onon yo yim…ìe am, min on mi…óo hulani on, sugu √±alaande he…ìunoonde feddeeji …óin"
  40,31,"Sugu mbowka yim…ìe Nuuhu …ìen, e Aadi'en, e Samuuda'en, e arnoo…ìe …ìaawo ma…ì…ìe …ìen\". Allah faandanaaki too√±ude jeyaa…ìe …ìen"
  40,32,"Ko onon yo yim…ìe am, min mi…óo hulani on, √ëalaande noddindirton"
  40,33,"√ëalnde huccitiroyton, ho…óon ndoga, hara da…óndoowo on alanaa on e Allah\". Kala mo Allah majjini, haray fewnoowo alanaa mo"
  40,34,"Gom…óii Yuusufu ardanii on e …ìannganduyeeji, ko adii, on seeraali e sikkitagol kon ko o addani on. Haa nde o faatinoo, wi'u…óon: \"Allah nultataa Nulaa…óo goo, …ìaawo makko\". Ko non majjinirta kala wono…óo fantinoowo sikkitii…óo"
  40,35,"∆Åen wenjiroo…ìe e Aayeeje Allah …óen ko aldaa e hujja ar…óo …ìe, [kuu…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen] mawnii tikkere ka Allah, e ka gom…óim…ìe …ìen. Ko wano non Allah notirta e …ìernde kala mawnintinii…óo dundarankeejo"
  40,36,"Fir'awna wi'i: \" Ko an yo Haamaana, mahanam sooro, no gasa mi yottoo …óate …óen"
  40,37,"…óate kammuuli …óin, mi ∆¥eewoya Rewetee…óo Muusaa On; sabu mi sikki mo fenoowo\". Ko wano non Fir'awna cu…óiranaa, golle makko bon…óe …óen; o sakkaa e laawol (peewal) ngol. Feere Fir'awna nden wonaano, si wanaa e hayrere"
  40,38,"[Gorko] gom…óin…óo on wi'i: \"Ko onon yo yim…ìe am, jokkee lam, mi fewna on e laawol peewal ngol"
  40,39,"Ko onon yo yim…ìe am, anndee …óam nguurndam aduna, ko dakamme-hun tun, ko laakara on woni, galle √±ii…ìal …óen"
  40,40,"Mo gollii bone, o yo…ìitetaake, si wanaa yeru makko; mo gollii kadi mo∆¥∆¥ere, foti ko gorko maa debbo, hara ko o gom…óin…óo, …ìen …óon naatay Aljanna, …ìe arsikoyee ton, ko aldaa e limoore"
  40,41,"Ko onon yo yim…ìe am, ko wa…ói si mi…óo nodda on e da…óal, hi…óon nodda lam e Yiite"
  40,42,"Hi…óon nodda lam e yeddugol Allah, sirkana Mo e ko mi alanaa …óum ganndal, hara non, min mi…óo nodda on e Foolu…óo, Suuroowo bakkaatu On"
  40,43,"Sikke alaa, wonnde ko noddoton lam e mun kon, dewal alanaa …óum aduna, wanaa laakara. E wonnde ruttorde men nden, ko ka Allah, e wonnde ko fantim…ìe …ìen, woni Yiite ngen"
  40,44,"Aray nde anndoton, ko mi yewtata on kon; mi fawa fiyaaku am on e Allah. Pellet, Allah ko Reenu…óo jeyaa…ìe …ìen"
  40,45,"Allah da…óndi mo, boneeji …ói …ìe fewjunoo, O fiiltii yim…ìe Fir'awna …ìen, ko …ìuri bonnde e lepte"
  40,46,"Yiite ngen, …ìe wee…ìitoyte e magge, bimmbi e kiikii…óe. √ëalnde Darngal daroytoo (wi'oyte): \"Naatee yim…ìe Fir'awna …ìen, ka …ìuri sa…ótude e lepte"
  40,47,"Janto tuma …ìe yeddondiroyta ka Yiite, lo'unoo…ìe …ìen wi'ana townitinoo…ìe …ìen: \"Menen, ko onon men jokkuunoo, taw si on du√±anay men ge…ìal e Yiite ngen"
  40,48,"Townitinoo…ìe …ìen wi'a: \"En fow, hi…óen e magge. Gom…óii Allah √±aawii hakkunde jeyaa…ìe …ìen"
  40,49,"Won…ìe ka Yiite …ìen kadi wi'ana ayninaa…ìe Jahannama …ìen: \"Toranee men Joomi mon, O hoynana men, √±alaande (wootere) e lepte …óen"
  40,50,"∆Åe wi'a: \"Nulaa…ìe mon …ìen ardanaano on e …ìanngannduyeeji?\" ∆Åe wi'a: \"Oo'owoye !\" [Ayninaa…ìe] …ìen wi'a: \"Awa toree, onon tigiri !\" Kono toraare heefer…ìe …ìen wonaali, si wanaa e majjere"
  40,51,"Pellet, Men wallay Nulaa…ìe Amen …ìen, e gom…óim…ìe …ìen, ka nguurndam aduna, e √ëalnde seedee…ìe …ìen daroytoo"
  40,52,"√±alnde de ngantinagol nafoytaa too√±unoo…ìe …ìen, hara kuddi hino woodani …ìe, e galle bon…óe"
  40,53,"Gom…óii Men okkii Muusaa ganndal [Tawreeta] ngal, Men ronini …ìi…ó…ìe Israa'iila …ìen, Deftere nden"
  40,54,"ko nde peewal e waaju, wonannde joomiraa…ìe haqqille …ìen"
  40,55,"Mu√±√±o tun, pellet, fodoore Allah nden ko goonga, insinano junuubi maa …óin, subbunhinano…óaa Joomi maa, kiikii…óe e bimmbi"
  40,56,"Pellet, wennjiroo…ìe e Aayeeje Allah …óen, ko aldaa e dalil ar…óo e ma…ì…ìe, alaa e …ìer…óe …óen, si wanaa mawnintinagol. ∆Åe yottotaako non, e …óum. Moolor Allah, Ko Kanko woni Nanoowo, Yi'oowo On"
  40,57,"Pellet, ko tagde kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin, …ìuri mawnude e dii tageendi yim…ìe …ìen. Kono ko …ìuri …óuu…óude e yim…ìe …ìen, …ìe anndaa"
  40,58,"Bun…óo e yi'oowo fotataa, gom…óim…ìe …ìen kadi golli mo∆¥∆¥u…ói, fotataa e bonnu…óo. Fan…óii ko waajitorton"
  40,59,"Pellet, Darngal, ko ko arata, sikke alaa e mu'un. Kono ko …ìuri …óuu…óude e yim…ìe …ìen, …ìe gom…óinaa"
  40,60,"Joomi mon daali: \"Toree Lam, Mi jaabinana on. Mawtinantoo…ìe rewugol Lam …ìen, ko pellet, …ìe naatoyay Jahannama, ko …ìe hoy…ìe"
  40,61,"Ko Allah wa…óirani on jemma on, ka fowto…óon e mun, e √±alorma on, yi'inoowo. Pellet, Allah ko Jom …ìural e yim…ìe …ìen, kono ko …ìuri …óuu…óude e yim…ìe …ìen, …ìe yettataa (neema)"
  40,62,"Ko On moo…óon Allah Joomi mon, woni Tagu…óo kala huunde. Rewetee…óo alaa, si wanaa Kanko. Ko honno firlitorta…óon (e …óum)"
  40,63,"Ko non …ìeya yeddaynoo…ìe Aayeeje Allah …óen, ferlisortenoo"
  40,64,"Ko Allah woni wa…óiran…óo on leydi ndin, √±ii…ìirde, kammu ngun, kippoodi, O mbaadini on - O mo∆¥∆¥ini mbaadiiji mon -, O arsiki on e laa…ìu…ói. Ko On moo…óon woni Allah Joomi mon; senaare woodanii Allah, Jey…óo winndere nden"
  40,65,"Ko Kanko woni wuur…óo On. Rewetee…óo alaa, si wanaa Kanko. Rewee Mo kisan; la…ì…ìinano Mo diina kan. Yettoore woodanii Allah, Jey…óo winndere nden"
  40,66,"Maaku: \"Min mi ha…óaama rewugol …óin …ói noddoton gaanin Allah, tuma nde …ìannganduyeeji …óin ari e am, immorde e Joomi am, mi yamiraama kadi, nde mi jebbilantoo, Jey…óo winndere nden"
  40,67,"Ko Kanko woni tagu…óo on e mbumbuldi, refti e to…ì…ìere (maniiyu), refti e he…ó…óere, refti O yaltiniri on penuu…ìe fii no yottoron cemmbe mon, e no laatoron nayee…ìe, - no e mo'on, ∆¥ettitetee…ìe ado …óum, - haa no yottoron lajal happaangal, belajo'o, on haqqilay"
  40,68,"Ko Kanko woni wuurnoowo e waroowo. Si O haajii e fiyaaku, ko O wi'anay mo tun: \"Laato\", o laatoo"
  40,69,"E a tinaali, …ìen yeddondirtee…ìe e Aayeeje Allah …óen, ko honno …ìe firlitoraa"
  40,70,"∆Åen fennu…ìe Deftere nden, e kon ko Men nuliri Nulaa…ìe Amen …ìen; …ìe aray anndude"
  40,71,"tuma kolombooje …óen wa…óoyaa e daa…óe ma…ì…ìe, e jolokooje(callalle) …óen, hara hi…ìe daasiree"
  40,72,ka nder wul…óam; refti …ìe hu…ì…ìoyee ka nder Yiite
  40,73,"Refti …ìe wi'anee: \"Ko honto woni …óin …ói kafidayno…óon"
  40,74,"Ko aldah e Allah?\" ∆Åe wi'a: \"∆äi majjitike men. Wurin, men wonaano ko adii, e rewugol hay huunde\". Ko hona nih Allah majjinirta heefer…ìe …ìen"
  40,75,"Ko wa…ói on …óum, ko ko weltorayno…óon kon ka hoore leydi, ko aldaa e goonga, e ko wewlirayno…óon kon"
  40,76,"Naatiree dame Jahannama …óen, luttugol ton. Nge bonii jaa∆¥orde wonande mawnintinii…ìe …ìen"
  40,77,"Mu√±√±o. Pellet, fodoore Allah nden, ko goonga. Ko si Men hollete yoga e ko Men fodi …ìe kon, maa hara Men ∆¥ettite (ado mun) ko ka Amen …ìe ruttirtee"
  40,78,"Gom…óii Men imminii Nulaa…ìe ado maa. Hino e ma…ì…ìe, …ìe Men sifani maa fii mun; hino ma…ì…ìe, …ìe Men sifanaaki ma fii mun. Haananaa Nulaa…óo, addugol Aaya, si wanaa e du≈ãayee Allah. Si yamiroore Allah nden arii, goonga √±aawirte meerente'en sooya nden √±alnde"
  40,79,"Ko Allah woni wa…óiran…óo On neemoraa…ói …óin ko wa…ó…óoron, √±aamon kadi e majji"
  40,80,"nafooje kadi hino woodani on e majji, e no yottoron e majji, haaju hittu…óo e berde mon. Ko e hoore majji e hoore laa…óe …óen, woni ko ronndete…óon"
  40,81,"Himo holla on maandeeji Makko …óin. Ko hon…óum e maandeeji Allah …óin, woni ko yeddoton"
  40,82,"E …ìee yiilaaki ka leydi, …ìe ndaara ko honno battane …ìeya ado ma…ì…ìe wattinirnoo? ∆Åen no …ìurunoo …ìe …óuude e sa…ótude doole e batteeji [wa…óaa…ói] ka leydi. Kono kon ko …ìe faggotonoo, duncanaano …ìe"
  40,83,"Nde Nulaa…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen addannoo…ìe …ìanngannduyeeji …óin, …ìe wewliri ganndal ko woni ka ma…ì…ìe kon. ∆Åe huu…ìitiraa kon ko …ìe jalkitaynoo"
  40,84,"Nde …ìe yi'unoo lepte Amen …óen, …ìe wi'i: \"Men gom…óinii Allah tun, men yeddii kon ko men wonunoo e sirkannde"
  40,85,"Kono gom…óinal ma…ì…ìe wonaano ko nafata …ìe, fewndo …ìe yi'unoo lepte Amen …óen; …óum ko laawol Allah non, gom…óii …óun yawtiino e jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen. Yeddu…ìe …ìen sooyi …óon nden √±alnde"